response.overview: On December 07, 2017, Refresh Park General Gymnasium in Yamaguchi hosted Day 16 of NJPW World Tag League 2017.  The main event featured CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Will Ospreay & Toru Yano) vs Los Ingobernables de Japon (EVIL, SANADA, Hiromu Takahashi & Tetsuya Naito).  The card also featured Killer Elite Squad (Davey Boy Smith Jr. & Lance Archer) vs Henare & Togi Makabe.  Other wrestlers on the show include Hirooki Goto, Tomohiro Ishii, and El Desperado, and more!
response.title: NJPW World Tag League 2017: Day 16
